## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not cover all aspects of the development process. The information is subject to the limitations of the sources used, which may include biases or outdated data. Additionally, the complexity of national development means that strategies effective in one context may not be applicable in another. Further research and localized studies are recommended for a more comprehensive understanding.